      Time-saving backlog management for fast-growing startups.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-screen-xl text-center">
      Our mission statement is simple: Keep your backlogs two sprints ahead.
    </p>
    <div
      class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center items-center">
      <Link
        href="#"
        href="https://calendly.com/sgmaca/sprintsahead-discovery-call"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex gap-1 items-center justify-center"
        rel="noopener">
        Schedule a Discovery Call
      </Link>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center items-center">
      <Link
        href="#"
        href="https://form.jotform.com/241597860233057"
